{"type": "article", "id": 28640, "title": "如果你在巴黎街头看到这些甜点，请不要吃到肚子里", "description": "它们的名字是 EAT ME，其实是呼吁减少浪费。", "date": "2016-06-24T06:54:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 521, "name": "街头艺术"}, {"id": 29358, "name": "Lor-K"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 163, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703181020Aact69LKoMZ3qkyv.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>披萨饼、肉串、蛋糕、三明治......这些甜点突然出现在了巴黎的街道上，上面的奶油、水果和蔬菜都清晰分明，还能看到寿司中间夹着的“三文鱼”和“黄瓜片”。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181007KQkmJVIBSL8RilG0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181008GDoOM9fTHYsl3kLR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181009O62j9wxgliYMEL5z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181009QVF0LWBRGkab1xSg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181010pGMWDbFJ73KYL2ns.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031810108Mr41Zxsi9Sf5CQk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181011EnTcadFhrfxt6zbm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181011w4k16hrSHzL2Kxeo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181011yCpHEQDNkwbGs2KL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181012OI27EeFjwWLAcU9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181012o9D7cahXnUurZ4Qe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181013h20ytVUfOlxPuAZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>这 12 组作品名叫 EAT ME，来自法国一位街头艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.lor-k.com/\">Lor-K</a>，她用废弃的床垫、地毯手工制作了这些“大餐”，比如动图中所示三角形披萨饼的做法，就是将一张方形的床垫切割，缝上红色的地毯和一道绒毛作为芝士边，最后再点上她用碎布料做的蘑菇、肉片和调料。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181014JGqRys7TvV2SOaWA.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56733524\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181015jD1gmkWKNoiadOTt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75305623\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">寿司。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181015SzA6TxgrVI2ECHi1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61912752\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181016bvr2tPi7M0pEdhZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61491443\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181017b94R1VKOHAkInsYG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74962519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">三明治。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181017pv4AnCUJdDE9TWuH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.586\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181018rLVYeXq6hZKjSwUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80515298\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Lor-K 背着剪裁工具、缝制工具、油漆等原料在城市里到处走，寻找丢掉的床垫来制作。她称，做这一件下来需要花费  2 到 6 个小时，具体做成什么样都是到了地方才考虑的。“我在路上准备我的食谱，到了那里决定炒什么菜。”</p>\n<p>令人惊讶的是，没有什么人在这个过程中对她进行干扰或阻拦，人们普遍忽略了她。最后的成品获得了很多关注和报道，尽管没有任何说明或标注，街道本身就是画廊。</p>\n<p>“我不介意它是否很脏，也不认为它很脏，我喜欢它所反映的城市，我们的浪费也是对我们生活的反映。”</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031810180h7G1tDArjIdN9cn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Lor-K 很擅长用废弃的物品在街上创作，这样也能最大范围吸引路过人的关注，更有社会效应。她曾经做的 NATURE MORTE 是用被丢掉的水果蔬菜做成花园里的装饰品一样，也是为了提醒浪费。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031810192A51IpHtVJPacfiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181019S9U5I246W3L1VqvO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>OBJETICIDE 也是用废弃的家具，红色的油漆涂抹在劈开的沙发、床和冰箱上，模拟了人体流血的样子，是用来反抗暴力。在 <a href=\"http://www.lor-k.com/\">Lor-K</a> 的个人主页里，你可以找到这些作品的照片。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703181020nW6RHhGCg4lFawZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.31481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.lor-k.com/\">Lor-K</a>、<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/french-artist-lor-k-street-food-discarded-mattresses-oversized-street-art-06-01-2016/\">designboom</a>、<a href=\"http://www.fastcodesign.com/3061140/this-artist-turns-dirty-old-mattresses-into-food-sculptures-and-they-look-delicious\">fastcodesign</a></p>\n\n\n"}